### ============================================
### PROJECTS (via BFF)
### ============================================

### List all projects
GET http://localhost:8080/projects

### Create a project
POST http://localhost:8080/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Fazenda Aurora",
  "location": "PR",
  "hectares": 200,
  "certifier": "Verra"
}

### Get a project by ID (SUBSTITUA <id>)
GET http://localhost:8080/projects/<id>

### Update a project (SUBSTITUA <id>)
PUT http://localhost:8080/projects/<id>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Fazenda Aurora Updated",
  "location": "SC",
  "hectares": 250,
  "certifier": "Verra"
}

### Delete a project (SUBSTITUA <id>)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/projects/<id>

### ============================================
### BATCHES (via BFF)
### ============================================

### List all batches
GET http://localhost:8080/batches

### Create a batch (SUBSTITUA <projectId>)
POST http://localhost:8080/batches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": "<projectId>",
  "tonsCO2": 40,
  "pricePerTon": 15,
  "status": "AVAILABLE"
}

### Get a batch by ID (SUBSTITUA <id>)
GET http://localhost:8080/batches/<id>

### Update a batch (SUBSTITUA <id>)
PUT http://localhost:8080/batches/<id>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": "<projectId>",
  "tonsCO2": 50,
  "pricePerTon": 18,
  "status": "SOLD"
}

### Delete a batch (SUBSTITUA <id>)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/batches/<id>

